data.enText: an official who lives in a foreign country as the senior representative there of his or her own country

data.chText: 英国驻意大利 / 罗马大使
data.enText: the British Ambassador to Italy/in Rome
a former ambassador to the UN

data.chText: 这种运动最好的大使就是运动员。
data.enText: The best ambassadors for the sport are the players.

tr: a diplomat of the highest rank
accredited as representative from one country to another

value.def: An ambassador is an important official who lives in a foreign country and represents his or her own country's interests there.

trans: 親善大使；亲善大使；形象大使；友好大使
